  <brief_title>Influence of Audiovisual Aids in the Preanesthetic Interview</brief_title>
  <official_title>Influence of Audiovisual Aids in the Preanesthetic Interview: A Comparison of the Effect of Face-to-face-interview Versus a Brochure and Video Assisted Interview</official_title>
